room_title: Escape room "Catch a Killer" by Escape Marquette in Marquette
room_address: 130 W Washington St Suite L-4 Marquette, MI 49855
room_description: You are a team of private investigators hired by the Hall family to look into the disappearance of their daughter, Alice, who went missing 3 weeks ago. Your mission is to investigate the office of Dr. Simon Jenkins, a therapist at New Beginnings Psychology Services. On the day Alice went missing she had an appointment with him, afterwards she was supposed to meet friends at the gym but never showed up. The family believes he is directly linked to her disappearance. Locate Alice's purse in order to solve the case and Catch a Killer.
